<HEAD>New Comedy Network Buys Reruns</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   MTV Networks, which owns cable TV's Nickelodeon
and a new all-comedy channel that will start next year, said
Tuesday it has bought rights to 15 former network shows, including
